{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_19","type":"mcp_tool_call","server":"remem","tool":"search","arguments":{"query":"memory demo ticket","limit":20,"include_stale":true},"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"mode\": \"compact\",\n  \"next_step\": {\n    \"ids\": [\n      53959,\n      54060,\n      57400,\n      71810,\n      53997,\n      57564,\n      53214,\n      53960,\n      53958,\n      54769,\n      66600,\n      39581,\n      65452,\n      57605,\n      56212,\n      58306\n    ],\n    \"reason\": \"Pass selected compact result IDs with source='memory' to fetch full details.\",\n    \"source\": \"memory\",\n    \"tool\": \"get_observations\"\n  },\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"has_more\": false,\n    \"limit\": 20,\n    \"next_offset\": null,\n    \"offset\": 0\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 53959,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 用户要完成任务 `12`：将 `12a` 收束为 Open Eagle Runner 开源首发方案 / open-source launch plan，并同步 continuity memory。]\\n\\nLicense posture 定为 `MPL-2.0 core + MIT examples + CC0/CC BY demo-media`，用 MPL-2.0 保护 core 文件级改动，同时降低 examples 和 demo media 复用门槛。\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/research/open-eagle-runner/workspace\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"License posture 定为 `MPL-2.0 core + MIT examples + CC0/CC BY demo-media`，用 MPL-2. — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-7678d92b5807d1a1\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-29 06:59\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 54060,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: Build the public bootstrap file/owner matrix for Open Eagle Runner and sync project memory, covering bootstrap lanes `bootstrap-01` to `bootstrap-04`,]\\n\\nRestricted `rights-ledger destination` values to exactly `docs/demo/ASSET_LICENSES.md`, `fixtures/README.md`, or `neither`, reducing ambi\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/research/open-eagle-runner/workspace\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"Restricted `rights-ledger destination` values to exactly `docs/demo/ASSET_LICENSES.md`, `fixtures/README. — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-34b6afe71f1996ce\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-29 07:26\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 57400,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 用户在 `looper` 中整理中文 X single-post 草稿，主题是 AI agent production trustworthiness、`testing harness`、`code]\\n\\n中文 X 草稿选择 `recommended_medium: single-post`，采用第二人称开头、第二段给数字和机制、第三段再归因与 URL，避免 emoji、TLDR、过度工整排比。内容策略拒绝空泛 AI 叙事，保留 `66 engineering tickets`、`TensorRT` 编译延迟降 `70%`、`context graphs`、`tmux`、`s\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm0000gn/T/chronicle/screen_recording\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"中文 X 草稿选择 `recommended_medium: single-post`， — decisions\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-9d2f6b8354301c01\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-30 11:11\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 71810,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: User wanted a persistent memory summary for a session whose last deliverable was a DocModel JSON market overview card for Long Island City / LIC real]\\n\\nCitation sources embedded in `data.citations` are ESRI Demographic Snapshot LIC Trade Area 2026, NYC DCP Population Projections Queens Bor\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om/om-generator/skills\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"Citation sources embedded in `data.citations` are ESRI Demographic Snapshot LIC Trade Area 2026, — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-a425bbf449f8a3a5\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-09 11:01\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 53997,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 完成任务 12b：为 open-eagle-runner launch 期公开资产生成 machine-readable asset rights and source manifest，]\\n\\n<item>`data/12b-demo-asset-rights-and-source-manifest.csv` 是 open-eagle-runner launch 公开资产的权利与来源清单，规模为 `38` 行 `19` 列。</item>\\n    <item>`13-public-repo-bootstrap-spec` 已是 `memory/TASKS.md` 中的下一主\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/research/open-eagle-runner/workspace\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"<item>`data/12b-demo-asset-rights-and-source-manifest.csv` 是 open-eagle-runner launch — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-3fca8a8385fe1d5f\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-29 07:09\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 57564,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: User needed a persistent memory summary of a Chronicle screen-recording session covering OM deployment troubleshooting, Gmail/Zoom coordination,]\\n\\nUser was simultaneously preparing for a Zoom demo meeting from Gmail while debugging OM deployment.\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm0000gn/T/chronicle/screen_recording\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"User was simultaneously preparing for a Zoom demo meeting from Gmail while debugging OM deployment. — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-f7f78ade2baeae4c\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-30 13:04\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 53214,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: User wanted a persistent memory summary of a read-only Claude Code session focused on `~/Desktop/code/work/mutil-om` OM generator layout architecture,]\\n\\nThe `28&7 OM` demo required `Market Overview` text plus image; the visible discussion argued against removing the text block entirely.\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj