from participants including `Yu Gao`, `Felix/XT`, and `irene c\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm0000gn/T/chronicle/screen_recording\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"`CRE Broker OM Generator` Gmail space contains high-signal Chinese demo review feedback from participants — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-5c5220c10a7bfb13\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-29 10:18\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 66600,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: Generate a persistent memory summary for a completed Claude Code/Codex screen-recording session covering AtlasCloud PR #281,]\\n\\n28and7 demo-cut issues include surfacing `21% Below Market Rent` and `$75K`, prioritizing `mark_to_market Upside` / `Below Market Rent` via `below_market_pct`, anc\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm0000gn/T/chronicle/screen_recording\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"28and7 demo-cut issues include surfacing `21% Below Market Rent` and `$75K`, — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-0bd759f31ff3eb57\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-06 09:22\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 39581,\n      \"preview\": \"长任务 agent workflow runtime 的接口应分层为 scheduler / operator / runtime / tool / skill / memory 六类角色。scheduler 只负责何时重入（cron、wakeup、event watch），输出 resume_ticket，不直接决定业务下一步；operator 是唯一推进任务图的控制面，负责基于 runtime_state、artifact、budget、review verdict 选择 done/retry/improve/wait/dispatch/handoff/join/needs_human；r\",\n      \"project\": \"agent-workflow-runtime-runner\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"Runtime interface layering for long-task orchestration\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"runtime-interface-layering\",\n      \"type\": \"architecture\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-21 04:58\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 65452,\n      \"preview\": \"R1588 评估轮（22:03 CST）：raw=116 → pool=4 (hot=2) → 0/4 通过 content contract → empty_reason=hard_anchor_fail (consecutive_empty=3)。候选全部 reject：@IntCyberDigest (sensational news 转发号 ‼️ + strong framing 受众错位)、@elder_plinius (Runic Magick meme 无技术锚点)、@uxkosta (interactive hero 设计图无工程讨论点)、@bridgemindai (GPT \",\n      \"project\": \"manual\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"Memory\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"x-reply-round-1588-2026-05-05\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-05 14:04\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 57605,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: User wanted a persistent memory summary for a Claude Code/Chronicle session covering a context-switch interval with Notion `harness skill`,]\\n\\nUser uses Notion as idea backlog, Warp as primary terminal, Claude Code inside Warp, Chrome for X/Zoom/demo pages, and X account `@mylifcc` analytic\",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm0000gn/T/chronicle/screen_recording\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"User uses Notion as idea backlog, Warp as primary terminal, Claude Code inside Warp, — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-94a583f5fde3267a\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-30 13:23\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 56212,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: User wanted a durable session memory for the Atlas CRE Studio / CRE Broker OM commercial real-estate OM workstream, capturing product decisions,]\\n\\n`Amenities Map` needs max-character truncation with whole-word cutoff, not naive character slicing. `om_generator_web` `ui` was ahead of `dev` \",\n      \"project\": \"/private/var/folders/h2/29bv07g91nqd40ybjj_vb6nm00